                        “Field commander of the Maidan”, “Terminator”- in such a way was Yu.Lutsenko called during Orange Revolution. He was one of the protest’s engine against falsification for honor of V.Yanukovych.

                        “Experience of the action “Ukraine without Kuchma” is completely valuable as training in setting of new Ukrainian government. Exactly tested there such methods, when opposition of different colors unites and gets result, were very important. Those 17 days of nice, gay, optimistic Maidan, still, for sure, are the best pages in my life, and, I think, for millions of those, who were there”, says Yu.Lutsenko.
                        At that moment Yu.Lutsenko was a very influencive person in Socialistic party. Giving honor for the leader of SPU Oleksandr Moroz, he states that the leader of the party destroyed his political future. “At that moment he was big, because he organized the only on the postsoviet surface Parliament left Party. He did a lot for our Constitution to be democratic, but then, he came to dependence from people for whom “Mark’s Capital” was so important as capital of Rinat Akhmetov”, - in such a way Yu.Lutsenko characterizes his attitude to the former leader of SPU.

                        Yuryi Vitaliyovych did a lot for Sociological Party to be the left party of the Western type. Such party was necessary for Ukraine. But he recognizes that for a long time he did not feel left illusions.” All of them went into the first months of work in the Ministry of Internal Affairs. As soon as I learned what is going on in the country’s economic, all my left illusions about the possibility of state regulation of economic, about state ruling of economic flew away immediately. That’s why, I still feel sorry for the left ideas of justice, support of weak, attitude to the minorities of any type, and absolutely do not trust in the recipes of the economics’ construction. They do not work. This is only the way to corruption”, -states he.
                        Yu.Lutsenko payed a great role in conjunction of attempts of opposition around the future President V.Yuschenko. “After we came to the second tour, the events on Maidan began. I went there. On Maidan…I represented Yu.Lutsenko. The political rada of Sociological Party gathered immediately. Voted: Maidan to be supported. In case it will loose,   in order the Party not to be forbidden, to send there physically a person- Yu.Lutsenko, but do not state this officially. Such an interesting story was. Eventually, I consider, that the key event of the Maidan was that O.Moroz reaped hand of V.Yuschenko’,-told in his interview Yuryi Vitaliyovych.

                        After the victory of V.Yuschenko, Yu.Lutsenko was proposed to take the position of the Ministry of Internal Affairs. “I became the first civil Minister of Internal Affairs. But, after this proposition, it was in a day before the parliament voting, I have not told anything to the wife. When Irina, together with million of people, learned, probably, this such a stunning piece of news during this day, she left home and came back at five o’clock in the morning, angry, as a panther. She came and said: “Yura, you either would be killed or imprisoned”. For luck, she guessed for the best side”, - so, with humor charachterized for him, reminds his assignment in the Ministry of Internal Affairs  Yu.Lutsenko.

                        Further for me a time of discoveries began. I learned a lot. “My principle is very simple:I  never took money either for opening or closing of deals, especially, if appointed. Earlier there was such practice: I know exactly how much cost positions prior me. To me one came and said: “How can you assign to Poltava not knowing whom? This costs three millions”. I honestly considered that I solve socially important issues. I never gave orders: ”Close this deal, because I was called”, -says Yu.Lutsenko about the times of his management   of the Ministry of Internal Affairs.

                        “The field commander of Maidan” was twice the Minister of Internal Affairs – in 2005-2006 and in 2007-2010. When V.Yanukovich came to power, the most difficult trials started in the life of Yu.Lutsenko.

