                        Speaking about the Revolution of Dignity, Yu.Lutsenko often recites the words of L.Kostenko:”Maidan is the place where Ukraine has met itself”.
                        For Yu.Lutsenko European Maidan begins earlier then those dramatic events, which were brought to the revolution. “With Roman Bezsmertnyi, Oleksandr Tretiakovim, Taras Stets’kiv,with dozens of young people we organized movent “The third Republic”.
                        We involved there intelligants and started to think how should be Ukraine after Yanukovich. And also how to pursue it to be without Yanukovich. It has been finished exactly at the moment of signing the Agreement about Europenian association. We started to work very easy. We wrote in Facebook, invited volunteers, put 300 posts around Kiev. After investments of Sasha Tretiakov, we published one and a half millions of brochures “What is EU”, few hundreds of strips and flags. I together with Ira were staying in the street and giving these flags, were giving strips in the underground. All town was covered by posts- only volunteer student’s movement. Later, when was announced that the signing would not be, there was a meeting in the office of “Bat’kivshina”. We gathered there without Yulia-she was still in the prison!-and started to discuss what to do. I said: “There would be 100 thousand”. Everybody looked at me like at crazy. “There would be 100 thousand,- I say,- but we only need to give an advertisement…Let’s raise people”. I was answered: “Yura, you were in the prison and are not aware. In best case ten.10 thousand will be. I again: “ There would be 100 thousand”. We diverged. I disconnected the phone. In the morning I woke up, I had red signs- missed calls: Klichko, Yatsenyuk, Tyagnibok, Klichko, Yatsenyuk, Tyagnibok…We came to Shevchenko Park. Really, then too many people gathered. 100 thousand who showed that we did not agree that the perspective of returning to the europenian home was taken. This was the first demonstration of Future Maidan”,-Yu.Lutsenko says in such a way about the events of that time.
                        Yuryi Vitaliyovich in the European choice, which made Ukrainian society, sees, first of all, the chance for the country. “I want we have a choice-to live upon standards of Berlin, Paris, Warsaw…To get oriented for any other European country. Freedom gives us such chance. Not guarantee, but chance. Yes, Europe, first of all not salaries and pensions, not roads and services. Europe-is the skill to take a responsibility on ourself. The European answers for his actions and inaction. Ukraine by its actions proved that we came back to Europe, from where we had been stolen 350 years ago. Today, those, who would act, could be able to return it the best world standards. If the quantity of the inactive were more, means, this experiment would fail. But I want to have freedom”, -states he.

                        After the victory of Maidan and V.Yanukovich escape Yuryi Lutsenko headed the electoral list of “Block Petra Poroshenko” and after the victory at the elections, he headed the biggest Parliament’s fraction. But of the key moments of his life started a little bit later, when in May 2016, the Supreme Rada voted for his assignment as a General Prosecutor of Ukraine. “I was convinced that only a person inside the system, with such shocks and human experience should break this only non reformed institute of totalitarian soviet repressions. What should I have done? First-to open the windows. Turn on the light. Now, at any position of the General Public Prosecutor’s Office one can reach only through the competition, which is done upon the norms of European Rada. Second: nowadays investigation and supervision are within two sections. This is the State investigation bureau and General Public Prosecutor’s Office. And this means, that one manager can not call anymore neither investigator no prosecutor and say:” Either you imprison or you are dead!” Third: 72% of positions (this year 80 %) are filled by people not from the system. And I am very proud of this: the grass will hit the asphalt.  Forth: the appraisal of work, reprimand, reproach and so on, is done not by the Prosecutor and not by his deputies- but only specially organized municipality of the Prosecutors, as in any other European country”, -Yuryi Lutsenko speaks in such a way about reforming of the Prosecutor’s Public Office.

                        Speaking about the achievements of the General Public Prosecutor’s Office during his work, Yuryi Vitaliyovych reminds not only about 260 corruptors, who already serve their sentences, and 4 milliards of dollars returned back to the budget funds. “I, as a General Prosecutor, am more proud of destroying of the punishment system of NKVS, which through misunderstanding was named GPO. Nowadays there is no more punishment monolit. And I consider, that my mission , as a person inside the system, was to come after militia and prison, after Maidan and government, and kill the cruelest, nonformed dinosaur of the Soviet Union. And to organize a new European constructure, which, by the way, received the highest mark in the European Rada”.
                        However, Yu.Lutsenko realizes, that to struggle against corruption only by punishment methods is not enough. Serious preventive measures are required, in order the corruption would not be possible. “As for Ukraine, it is a big ship, which hold was recently completely filled by water. And when the General Prosecutor’s Office pump water by hand pump it is a hard work. It is eternal. That’s why, probably, it is important that except few thousand of sentences for corruption, which we already have, except this pump, we tried to close holes in our ship. I mean to close the main sources of corruption, which not depending from how many have been already arrested, continue to generate this deadly poison for our country”, -he states.

                        Yu.Lutsenko names the state sector the main source of corruption- 3600 state enterprises, from which two thirds are not profitable.  The second problem is the custom. And he sees the solution of the problem in the technological novelties. Electronical scanners, special procedures of check between neighbor countries. As a result – 30 % of incomes, which are now in the pockets of the rustlers, will come to the treasury of the country.The third source of corruption, according the opinion of Lutsenko, -licensees for bosoms.  Amber, sand, oil, gas, - all should be sold only at open auctions.
                        However, at the today’s stage Ukraine has what to be proud of in plan of the preventive struggle with corruption.  “Very important decisions have been taken after Maidan. The biggest source of corruption was always the return of VAT export: the rollbacks were 40 %. Now this is automatic money, 98% requests are satisfied. State purchases which are now done by computer system ProZorro - is also a huge breakout. Western experts apprise in 3-4 millions dollars of yearly earnings only from those two closed holes. Also the government has already developed the mechanism of open auctions for licensees.   It is necessary to have only a political desire not to do exceptions, -summarizes Yu.Lutsenko.


